Trading on SP500

Now were going to load the entire SP500 stocks into our list and backtest the momentum strategy on that. So lets first load the data.

Here we have the same basic principle as before but now well also visualize a bit whats going on. We can show the price movements along with the indicators we are using for our decision making.

chartSeries(mylist$AMAT)

In this example well show the development of Microsoft with momentum and volatility over a 90 day horizon.

chartSeries(mylist$MSFT, TA="addMomentum(n=90);addVolatility(n=90)")
